<head>
    <style>

        .tooltip {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 5px;
            left: 0;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .tooltip .tooltiptext {
            visibility: hidden;
            width: 220px;
            background-color: #333;
            color: #b5c91a;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 5px 0;
            position: absolute;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .tooltip:hover .tooltiptext {
            visibility: visible;
        }

        .icon {
            width:36px;
            height:36px;
            margin:1.1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<div class="tooltip">
    <img class="icon" src="detective.png" alt="Detective info">
    <span class="tooltiptext">Somewhere in the page there is one hidden cheat button that plays the best move for you. If you find it, dont spam clicks, it needs some time to think it</span>
</div>
